column2: select m.ra, m.dec, p.objid, p.g, p.r,   g.h_alpha_flux, g.nii_#_flux from MyDB.galaxyData as m join GalSpecLine as g join galSpecInfo as i on g.specobjid = i.specobjid join photoObj as p ON p.specobjid = g.specobjid join dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) n on p.objid=n.objid join specObj s on p.objid=s.bestobjid and s.Class= &&& and s.z >= # and g.h_alpha_flux > # and g.nii_#_flux > # and g.h_alpha_flux_err < g.h_alpha_flux and g.nii_#_flux_err < g.nii_#_flux and i.subclass != &&&
